# MIMIC-CXR chest X-ray images for lesion segmentation (cxr_lesion model).
#
# Layout:
#   data/mimic_cxr/{patient_id}/{study_id}/*.jpg|png
#
# Example (PhysioNet MIMIC-CXR-JPG export):
#   data/mimic_cxr/p10000032/s50414267/00000001.jpg
#
# Use model: cxr_lesion (torchxrayvision pretrained pathology localization)
